== 0.5.0 / 2009-12-05

Updates for Tap-0.19.0

== 0.4.0

* added short options to load/dump csv
* added Gate join
* added Null task
* added Stream task for stream loading
* updated load/yaml to only load a single document
* added stream/yaml for stream loading documents
* added Profiler middleware

== 0.3.0 / 2009-06-17

* added load/dump csv tasks
* updated glob task with include/exclude filters
* updated load/yaml with stream loading
* removed argv task
* removed FileTask

== 0.2.0 / 2009-05-25

Updates for use with Tap-0.17.0

* added configurable inspect method to inspect

== 0.1.0 / 2009-03-23

Initial release with:

* dump/load YAML tasks
* inspect/argv tasks
